2011-09-08T05:41:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/chroma-ate-inc-august-sales-fall-21-44-table-2360-tt.html
CHROMA ATE INC (2360)  said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 21.44% to NT$447,037,000 from NT$569,050,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            447,037          569,050    
YOY%             -21.44%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           4,071,838        3,859,338   
YOY%              5.51%  
=================================================================
 